Out of the way, Mei. I can't close the door with you there.

65
00:06:54,752 --> 00:06:55,920
Acorns.

66
00:06:56,087 --> 00:06:57,669
橡果子
Dad, acorns are falling from the ceiling.

67
00:06:57,669 --> 00:06:59,252
有很多橡果子掉到屋里
Dad, acorns are falling from the ceiling.

68
00:06:58,589 --> 00:07:01,296
从上面掉下来的
Falling from the ceiling.

69
00:07:01,551 --> 00:07:03,219
Hmm.

70
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:08,386
该不会是我们家有松鼠吧
Maybe squirrels live here.

71
00:07:08,307 --> 00:07:10,388
松鼠？
- Squirrels?    - Squirrels?

72
