放这里，我这就开门
Oh, right, the radio. In here's good, I guess.

76
00:07:20,987 --> 00:07:23,531
小月，你去把后门打开
- Satsuki, open the back of the house?    - Okay.

77
00:07:23,234 --> 00:07:24,235
好

78
00:07:23,698 --> 00:07:27,201
去了就看得到
- Can you find the back door?    - Of course!

79
00:07:27,368 --> 00:07:28,244
(GIGGLING)

80
