快点
Come on!

81
00:07:29,829 --> 00:07:32,369
等人家嘛
Hey, wait for me!

82
00:07:33,332 --> 00:07:35,460
快点
Well, hurry it up, then.

83
00:08:13,039 --> 00:08:15,124
进去罗
- Let's go.    - Hmph!

84
00:08:26,511 --> 00:08:28,717
浴室
- The bath.    - Yep.

85
00:08:34,101 --> 00:08:35,519
不见了
I think they're gone.

86
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:36,938
不见了
(GASPS)

87
00:08:37,104 --> 00:08:38,356
Hey, you found the bath.

88
00:08:38,143 --> 00:08:39,644
这间是浴室
Dad, something's running around in here.

89
00:08:39,644 --> 00:08:41,146
爸爸，有怪东西
Dad, something's running around in here.

90
00:08:40,483 --> 00:08:42,401
松鼠吗？
- More squirrels?    - I don't think so.

91
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:43,231
不知道

92
00:08:42,568 --> 00:08:46,614
不像蟑螂也不像老鼠
They're not bugs or mice, either. They were black, and they were all over the place.

93
00:08:46,192 --> 00:08:48,699
只知道是一堆黑色的东西
Hmm. Let's have a look.

94
00:08:59,126 --> 00:09:02,208
有没有？
- Ah.    - So?

95
00:09:02,004 --> 00:09:05,128
那一定是〝灰尘精灵〞
It was probably just some soot gremlins.

96
00:09:04,298 --> 00:09:07,051
灰尘精灵
What do you mean, “gremlins”? Like the ones in my book?

97
00:09:06,379 --> 00:09:07,338
画册里有吗？

98
00:09:07,218 --> 00:09:08,553
有啊
Well, it could be ghosts,

99
00:09:08,423 --> 00:09:12,765
今天天气那么好　不可能会有鬼的
but ghosts don't usually like to come out on nice days like this.

100
00:09:15,309 --> 00:09:19,350
我们从光的地方　一下子进到暗的地方
Normally, you can't see soot gremlins, but every once in a while,

101
00:09:18,187 --> 00:09:22,187
眼睛就会发昏　灰尘精灵就会跑出来
when you go from a bright place to a dark one, you can catch a glimpse of them.

102
00:09:21,774 --> 00:09:23,359
原来是这样啊
So that's it.

103
00:09:23,359 --> 00:09:24,944
原来是这样啊
Come out, come out…

104
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:27,233
灰尘精灵快点滚出来
BOTH: Wherever you are!

105
00:09:26,904 --> 00:09:29,133
你要躲着不出来　我就把你眼睛挖出来！
BOTH: Come out, come out, wherever you are!

106
00:09:29,133 --> 00:09:31,362
你要躲着不出来　我就把你眼睛挖出来！
(WHOOSHING)

107
00:09:31,534 --> 00:09:34,829
(LAUGHING)

108
00:09:35,621 --> 00:09:38,374
好了，去做事
Hey, I need your help. It looks like somebody's hidden

109
00:09:37,368 --> 00:09:41,372
上二楼的楼梯　到底在哪里呢？
the stairs to the top floor of the house.

110
00:09:40,668 --> 00:09:41,711
What?

111
00:09:41,877 --> 00:09:43,606
你们两个去把楼梯找出来
Can you find the stairs and open all the windows up there?

112
00:09:43,606 --> 00:09:45,335
然后把二楼的窗户打开
Can you find the stairs and open all the windows up there?

113
00:09:44,964 --> 00:09:47,128
好
Yeah!

114
00:09:46,257 --> 00:09:48,593
人家也要
Wait for me!

115
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,886
(GRUNTING)

116
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,142
Nope.

117
00:09:56,309 --> 00:09:58,348
厕所
The toilet!

118
00:10:00,391 --> 00:10:02,143
甚么？
Not here.

119
00:10:03,691 --> 00:10:07,107
甚么？
- Nothing here.    - Nothing here.

120
00:10:09,447 --> 00:10:11,194
甚么？
- Nope.    - Nope.

121
00:10:10,656 --> 00:10:13,743
甚么？
(LAUGHING)

122
00:10:13,909 --> 00:10:17,325
甚么？
Ahh!

123
00:10:18,456 --> 00:10:20,333
没有
Nope.

124
00:10:20,499 --> 00:10:23,461
没有
Nope. Hey!

125
00:10:29,884 --> 00:10:31,469
(CREAKING)

126
00:10:31,636 --> 00:10:34,384
小美，找到了
Mei, I found the stairs.

127
00:10:36,766 --> 00:10:38,643
(GASPS)

128
00:10:40,269 --> 00:10:42,104
乌漆抹黑的
It's pitch-black.

129
00:10:42,104 --> 00:10:43,939
乌漆抹黑的
Maybe it's the soot gremlins.

130
00:10:43,351 --> 00:10:45,270
灰尘精灵呢？

131
00:10:51,989 --> 00:10:54,362
橡果子
An acorn.

132
00:10:59,914 --> 00:11:05,206
灰尘精灵快点滚出来
Come out, come out, wherever you are!

133
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:07,296
(RUSTLING)

134
00:11:42,832 --> 00:11:45,413
灰尘精灵
We know you're in here, soot gremlins.

135
00:11:45,459 --> 00:11:47,712
你在不在？
Come on out.

136
00:11:48,838 --> 00:11:50,172
(GASPS)

137
00:12:09,942 --> 00:12:12,194
KUSAKABE: (GRUNTS) Okay, lift.

138
00:12:12,361 --> 00:12:17,153
爸爸，真的有怪东西
Dad, come here! There's definitely something weird in this house!

139
00:12:16,657 --> 00:12:19,155
那真是太棒了
That's great.

140
00:12:18,367 --> 00:12:20,974
爸爸从小就梦想　能够住在鬼屋里面
I've always wanted to live in a haunted house ever since I was a little boy.

141
00:12:20,974 --> 00:12:23,581
爸爸从小就梦想　能够住在鬼屋里面
BOTH: Oh!

142
00:12:23,748 --> 00:12:24,623
Ahh!

143
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:27,330
糟了
(CRASH)

144
00:13:12,254 --> 00:13:15,466
抓到了！姐姐
I caught one! Satsuki, look!

145
00:13:22,181 --> 00:13:24,809
- Ah!    - Oof!

146
00:13:26,060 --> 00:13:27,019
Hi.

147
00:13:27,186 --> 00:13:28,062
(SHRIEKS)

148
00:13:28,229 --> 00:13:30,393
小美
Mei?

149
00:13:30,689 --> 00:13:33,234
(PANTING)

150
00:13:33,442 --> 00:13:35,277
Oh.

151
00:13:35,903 --> 00:13:38,197
Whoa. Hey!

152
00:13:39,073 --> 00:13:40,074
(LAUGHING)

153
00:13:40,241 --> 00:13:42,322
好活泼啊
What a ball of energy!

154
00:13:41,826 --> 00:13:44,411
这位是一直照顾这个家
This is our neighbor. She takes care of this house.

155
00:13:44,282 --> 00:13:45,366
住在隔壁的婆婆

156
00:13:44,578 --> 00:13:47,368
婆婆今天是来帮忙的
She said you can call her “Granny” if you'd like.

157
00:13:47,248 --> 00:13:50,459
我叫做小月，这是我妹妹小美
I'm Satsuki, and that's Mei. Nice to meet you.

158
00:13:50,163 --> 00:13:51,247
婆婆好

159
00:13:50,626 --> 00:13:53,458
好，你们好啊
Well, it's nice to meet you, too.

160
00:13:53,546 --> 00:13:56,377
这孩子真是聪明伶俐
What nice manners you have.

161
00:13:56,006 --> 00:13:58,421
如果你们不急着搬进来
I'm sorry I didn't have time

162
00:13:57,967 --> 00:14:00,761
我还打算请人先收拾一下呢
to clean up more before you got here.

163
00:14:00,928 --> 00:14:02,638
这样子已经很好了
KUSAKABE: No, it's fine.

164
00:14:02,638 --> 00:14:04,348
这样子已经很好了
GRANNY: We've been busy in the rice fields,

165
00:14:03,343 --> 00:14:06,262
现在这时田里农事很忙碌呢

166
00:14:04,515 --> 00:14:09,265
不过我还是偶尔会来打扫
but I did manage to keep the place well-dusted, as you can see.

167
00:14:09,144 --> 00:14:12,314
小美，妳手怎么脏兮兮的？
Mei, your hands are filthy. What on earth did you do?

168
00:14:11,476 --> 00:14:12,435
怎么弄的？

169
00:14:12,481 --> 00:14:15,229
灰尘精灵跑掉了
I caught a soot gremlin, but he got away.

170
00:14:14,441 --> 00:14:17,315
妳看妳的脚
Ahh! Your feet!

171
00:14:20,406 --> 00:14:21,365
(GASPS)

172
00:14:21,490 --> 00:14:23,033
我的脚也脏兮兮的
Mine are black, too!

173
00:14:23,033 --> 00:14:24,577
我的脚也脏兮兮的
Ah…

174
00:14:25,323 --> 00:14:29,243
哎呀呀！

175
00:14:31,166 --> 00:14:34,374
看样子是煤煤虫在作怪
You've got soot sprites in your house.

176
00:14:34,211 --> 00:14:35,835
煤煤虫？
Soot sprites? The black puff balls? About this big?

177
00:14:35,835 --> 00:14:37,460
你说的煤煤虫是不是会
Soot sprites? The black puff balls? About this big?

178
00:14:37,548 --> 00:14:39,508
〝哇啦哇啦〞的乱跑啊
They scurry everywhere when you enter a room?

179
00:14:39,508 --> 00:14:41,468
〝哇啦哇啦〞的乱跑啊
That's right.

180
00:14:41,255 --> 00:14:42,298
是啊

181
00:14:41,635 --> 00:14:45,343
它们专门跑到没人住的旧房子里
They live in old, empty houses

182
00:14:44,805 --> 00:14:49,476
然后弄得满屋子的灰尘和煤灰
and run all over the place, covering everything with dirt.

183
00:14:49,643 --> 00:14:53,434
我小时候也有看过
I used to be able to see them when I was your age.

184
00:14:53,314 --> 00:14:57,397
想不到妳们也看到
So you've seen them, too. That's very interesting.

185
00:14:56,984 --> 00:14:59,403
婆婆，它们是妖怪吗？
So they're a kind of ghost, then?

186
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:04,195
其实也没什么好怕的
Don't worry, dear. They're nothing to be afraid of.

187
00:15:03,324 --> 00:15:07,281
只要对它们笑笑　它们就不会害人
If they decide you're nice people, they won't harm you,

188
00:15:06,869 --> 00:15:10,326
住上一阵子之后　它们自然就会不见
and after a while, they'll just go away.

189
00:15:09,371 --> 00:15:11,123
I bet they're up in the rafters right now,

190
00:15:11,202 --> 00:15:15,711
说不定它们已经在天花板上　讨论该搬去哪里了
having a talk about whether or not they should move out.

191
00:15:15,878 --> 00:15:18,589
(JABBERING)

192
00:15:20,299 --> 00:15:23,510
小美，它们很快就会不见了
- Hear that, Mei? They're gonna move out.    - I don't want them to leave.

193
00:15:23,256 --> 00:15:24,257
不好玩

194
00:15:23,677 --> 00:15:26,467
可是要是来这么一大堆　该怎么办？
What if a huge one came chasing after you?

195
00:15:26,513 --> 00:15:28,344
人家才不怕那些
So what? I'm not afraid.

196
00:15:28,098 --> 00:15:30,267
是吗？
Right. Then you can go to the bathroom

197
00:15:29,387 --> 00:15:32,473
那以后晚上　姐姐就不陪妳上厕所
by yourself in the middle of the night.

198
00:15:32,102 --> 00:15:34,021
(LAUGHING)

199
00:15:34,188 --> 00:15:35,189
Come on, girls.

200
00:15:34,392 --> 00:15:36,894
来来⋯快来打扫吧
Let's get to work. Who'd like to fetch some water for the pump?

201
00:15:36,894 --> 00:15:39,397
妳们去河边打点水回来吧
Let's get to work. Who'd like to fetch some water for the pump?

202
00:15:39,068 --> 00:15:40,440
河边啊
I'll go get it.

203
00:15:40,444 --> 00:15:41,941
人家也要去
I'll go, too!

204
00:15:42,029 --> 00:15:44,239
(LAUGHING)

205
00:15:44,907 --> 00:15:47,701
小美，妳在一边等着
Mei, wait there, okay?

206
00:15:56,210 --> 00:15:59,208
有没有抓到鱼？
Did you catch a fish?

207
00:16:04,969 --> 00:16:08,180
(GRUNTING)

208
00:16:08,347 --> 00:16:09,598
(SQUEALING)

