00:51:20,332 --> 00:51:21,541
(PLINK)

606
00:51:24,711 --> 00:51:27,506
(GRUMBLING)

607
00:51:30,050 --> 00:51:32,715
等我一下
Oh, wait a minute.

608
00:51:37,182 --> 00:51:39,893
这个借你
Here. Try this.

609
00:51:40,060 --> 00:51:44,476
快点啊　小美快要掉下来了啦
Hurry. Mei's slipping.

610
00:51:45,857 --> 00:51:48,151
(GRUNTS)

