I saw him, too!

636
00:54:58,883 --> 00:55:02,053
好棒啊
(GIRLS LAUGHING)

637
00:55:01,548 --> 00:55:04,973
好吓人啊
(CROAKING)

638
00:55:05,140 --> 00:55:06,933
