It was filled with acorns.

647
00:55:43,178 --> 00:55:44,429
(GASP)

648
00:55:44,596 --> 00:55:45,597
Ahh.

649
00:55:46,264 --> 00:55:47,432
(CHUCKLING)

650
00:55:47,640 --> 00:55:50,764
我们想家里院子　变成森林的话一定很棒
"We wanted to grow a beautiful forest with the acorns,

651
00:55:50,518 --> 00:55:53,772
所以就把它们洒在院子里
“so we planted them in your garden out back, but…”

652
00:55:53,684 --> 00:55:54,518
不过

653
00:55:53,897 --> 00:55:56,775
它们现在都还没有发芽
