00:56:01,488 --> 00:56:04,094
就好像猴子螃蟹大战　里面那个螃蟹一样啊
it's starting to make her crabby.

658
00:56:04,094 --> 00:56:06,701
就好像猴子螃蟹大战　里面那个螃蟹一样啊
Here's a picture of Mei as a crab.

659
00:56:06,868 --> 00:56:09,621
(CHUCKLING)

660
00:56:09,788 --> 00:56:11,831
学校很快就要放暑假了
Summer vacation is almost here,

661
00:56:11,831 --> 00:56:13,875
学校很快就要放暑假了
and I can't wait to play outside with you.

662
00:56:12,703 --> 00:56:16,628
希望妈妈的病　能够快点好起来好吗？
Please get well soon. Love, Satsuki.

663
00:56:15,831 --> 00:56:18,505
小月
(GIRLS LAUGHING)

664
00:56:20,131 --> 00:56:23,343
Get ready, and… up!

665
00:56:23,510 --> 00:56:24,386
(SHRIEKING)

666
00:56:24,552 --> 00:56:25,887
(LAUGHING)

667
00:56:26,054 --> 00:56:28,640
要关灯了
