00:56:28,807 --> 00:56:32,598
爸爸，明天会不会发芽？
Do you think that they'll sprout tomorrow?

670
00:56:32,143 --> 00:56:33,640
这个问题呀
I don't know.

671
00:56:33,311 --> 00:56:35,814
我看要问大龙猫才会知道
You should ask the Totoro. He would know.

672
00:56:36,022 --> 00:56:37,686
晚安
Good night, girls.

673
00:56:37,774 --> 00:56:39,609
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)

674
00:57:25,864 --> 00:57:27,736
小美
Mei.

675
00:57:27,824 --> 00:57:29,742
(GROANING)

676
00:57:44,924 --> 00:57:47,798
那是我们种橡果子的地方
That's where we planted the acorns.

677
00:59:17,767 --> 00:59:20,163
太棒了！
