01:02:17,238 --> 01:02:20,908
草壁先生在吗？电报
Mr. KUSAKABE? Telegram!

696
01:02:21,033 --> 01:02:23,698
草壁先生在家吗？
Mr. KUSAKABE?

697
01:02:23,782 --> 01:02:26,664
有您的电报
A telegram for you.

698
01:02:26,831 --> 01:02:29,829
没人在家啊
Huh. No one's home.

699
01:02:33,629 --> 01:02:35,506
(TRAMPLING)

700
01:02:35,673 --> 01:02:37,963
婆婆
MEI: Granny!

701
01:02:41,841 --> 01:02:44,636
我在这儿
I'm over here.

702
01:02:45,308 --> 01:02:48,598
长成这个样就能吃了
This one's ready to eat.

703
01:02:47,977 --> 01:02:50,521
(GRUNTING)

704
01:02:51,522 --> 01:02:52,982
(SNAP)

705
01:02:56,444 --> 01:02:58,608
婆婆，那这个呢？
What about this one, Granny?

706
01:02:58,321 --> 01:02:59,676
可以
Try it.

707
01:02:59,676 --> 01:03:01,032
可以
(GRUNTING)

708
01:03:01,199 --> 01:03:02,200
(SNAP)

709
01:03:05,745 --> 01:03:09,744
婆婆你的这块田　好像是一座宝山啊
Wow, Granny. Your garden is just like a market.

710
01:03:09,290 --> 01:03:12,831
来，休息一下喘口气
We've picked enough, haven't we? Let's take a rest.

711
01:03:18,670 --> 01:03:21,631
已经冰透了
Mmm. Nice and cold.

712
01:03:21,177 --> 01:03:23,763
那我要吃了
Mark, get set, go!

713
01:03:32,021 --> 01:03:33,768
好好吃啊
It's delicious.

714
01:03:33,481 --> 01:03:36,359
真的呀
I'm glad you like it. They're very good for you.

715
01:03:35,687 --> 01:03:37,751
这是因为经常被太阳晒
They've soaked up lots of vitamins and sunshine.

716
01:03:37,751 --> 01:03:39,816
对身体非常健康的啊
They've soaked up lots of vitamins and sunshine.

717
01:03:40,196 --> 01:03:43,282
对妈妈的身体也有益吗？
- Would they help Mom get better?    - Of course they would.

718
01:03:42,610 --> 01:03:43,695
当然啦

719
01:03:43,449 --> 01:03:45,553
只要是　吃了婆婆田里种的东西
If your mom eats my vegetables, I bet she'd get well right away.

720
01:03:45,553 --> 01:03:47,657
身体就会好啦
If your mom eats my vegetables, I bet she'd get well right away.

721
01:03:47,370 --> 01:03:50,577
这个星期六　我妈妈就会回来了
That's great, Granny. Mom's coming home on Saturday.

722
01:03:50,414 --> 01:03:52,871
妈妈要跟我一起睡觉啊
She's going to sleep with me in my bed.

723
01:03:52,708 --> 01:03:56,879
是吗？　马上就要出院了
Oh, good! She's finally leaving the hospital, is she?

724
01:03:56,875 --> 01:03:58,962
不算是真正的出院
No. The doctor wants her to get used to the new house a little at a time.

725
01:03:58,962 --> 01:04:01,050
星期一还得回去复诊
No. The doctor wants her to get used to the new house a little at a time.

726
01:04:00,879 --> 01:04:03,594
还没有那么快好
- She goes back on Monday.    - Is that so?

727
01:04:02,839 --> 01:04:04,632
这样吗？

728
01:04:03,761 --> 01:04:06,885
那可要多吃点东西补一补了
We'll feed her lots of my vegetables while she's here.

729
01:04:06,848 --> 01:04:10,805
我要把我自己摘的　粟米给妈妈吃
I'll give her the corn that I picked. That will make her better.

730
01:04:10,643 --> 01:04:13,855
那她一定会很高兴的
- I bet that will do her wonders.    - Yep.

731
01:04:21,696 --> 01:04:23,906
电报
Here. The postman left us your telegram.

732
01:04:23,276 --> 01:04:24,569
你们不在　所以邮差送去我家
A telegram?

733
01:04:24,569 --> 01:04:25,862
给我们的
A telegram?

734
01:04:29,245 --> 01:04:32,619
婆婆　我爸爸不到傍晚不回来
What should I do with it, Granny? Dad won't be home till evening.

735
01:04:32,331 --> 01:04:35,663
快打开看吧　要是急事耽搁就不好了
Better open it. Might be an emergency.

736
01:04:35,376 --> 01:04:37,461
Mmm-hmm.

737
