发电处七国山医院
“Please contact Shichikokuyama.”

738
01:04:42,758 --> 01:04:44,468
七国山医院送来的
Shichikokuyama! It's from Mom's hospital!

739
01:04:44,468 --> 01:04:46,178
那就是从妈妈的医院
Shichikokuyama! It's from Mom's hospital!

740
01:04:45,882 --> 01:04:48,760
难道妈妈发生了什么事
Something must have happened to her.

741
01:04:49,974 --> 01:04:51,369
婆婆，怎么办？
We have to get to the hospital right away, Granny.

742
01:04:51,369 --> 01:04:52,764
医院要我们跟他们联络
We have to get to the hospital right away, Granny.

743
01:04:52,602 --> 01:04:54,643
你别紧张，冷静一点
Okay. Calm down. First, we need to get in touch with your father.

744
01:04:54,643 --> 01:04:56,684
知不知道爸爸上班的地方？
Okay. Calm down. First, we need to get in touch with your father.

745
01:04:56,397 --> 01:04:58,128
爸爸研究室的电话号码　我是知道
I know his phone number at the university, but we don't have a phone.

746
01:04:58,128 --> 01:04:59,859
可是没有电话可打呀
I know his phone number at the university, but we don't have a phone.

747
01:04:59,854 --> 01:05:02,525
勘太　你带小月去打电话
Kanta, take Satsuki to your uncle's house and let her use the phone.

748
01:05:02,525 --> 01:05:05,197
勘太　你带小月去打电话
Mmm-hmm.

749
01:05:09,535 --> 01:05:12,788
小美妳留下来陪婆婆
Mei, you need to stay here with me!

750
01:05:21,339 --> 01:05:24,629
小美妳回去婆婆那里
Mei, go back and stay with Granny!

751
01:06:00,874 --> 01:06:04,465
请你接市外电话
Hello? I'd like to place a long-distance call, please.

752
01:06:04,590 --> 01:06:08,673
