我爸爸⋯　麻烦请草壁先生听电话
I mean, I need to speak to Mr. KUSAKABE.

760
01:06:25,569 --> 01:06:27,859
我叫做草壁月
My name is Satsuki KUSAKABE.

761
01:06:31,409 --> 01:06:33,781
爸爸，是我，小月
Hello, Dad? Is that you? It's Satsuki.

762
01:06:33,703 --> 01:06:35,783
怎么了？
