01:08:27,524 --> 01:08:29,693
走吧
(CRYING)

799
01:08:29,860 --> 01:08:34,652
姊姊大坏蛋！
She's so mean!

800
01:08:33,823 --> 01:08:36,784
(CRYING)

801
01:09:00,141 --> 01:09:02,432
衣服该收收了
Come on, girls. Let's put the laundry away.

802
01:09:02,432 --> 01:09:04,724
别这么沮丧
Come on, girls. Let's put the laundry away.

803
01:09:04,186 --> 01:09:07,731
婆婆不是过来帮忙了吗
Oh, don't be sad. Granny's here to help.

804
01:09:07,685 --> 01:09:10,897
打起精神

805
01:09:15,406 --> 01:09:19,906
你爸爸说他今天　要留在医院过夜
Don't worry. Your father is going to stop by the hospital.

806
01:09:20,369 --> 01:09:23,659
妳妈妈不过是感冒而已
The doctors say your mom just has a cold.

807
01:09:23,622 --> 01:09:27,126
下个星期六一定会回来的
She should be home next Saturday.

808
01:09:31,172 --> 01:09:32,923
之前也是这样
This is just like last time.

809
01:09:33,048 --> 01:09:37,178
医生说只要住数天就会好了
They said Mom just had a little cold, she'd be home in a few days.

810
01:09:36,631 --> 01:09:38,758
而且那次也是说得了感冒

811
01:09:38,888 --> 01:09:41,886
我妈妈要是死了该怎么办
Granny, what will we do if she dies?

812
01:09:41,348 --> 01:09:43,805
小月
Satsuki!

813
01:09:43,601 --> 01:09:46,353
我妈妈要是死了那我们⋯
Maybe she's dead already.

814
01:09:46,353 --> 01:09:49,106
我妈妈要是死了那我们⋯
(CRYING)

815
01:09:49,607 --> 01:09:52,730
妳放心，不要乱想
Now, don't say that, sweetheart.

816
01:09:52,772 --> 01:09:57,652
妳妈妈哪舍得下　妳们这些可爱的孩子
How could she ever leave such sweet girls like you?

817
01:09:57,364 --> 01:09:59,658
别哭了别哭了
Oh, don't cry.

818
01:09:59,658 --> 01:10:01,952
别哭了别哭了
Don't cry. It's all right.

819
01:10:01,697 --> 01:10:03,782
在妳爸爸回来之前
I'll stay here until your father comes home. Okay? Okay?

820
01:10:03,782 --> 01:10:05,868
婆婆都会陪着妳的　好不好呀
I'll stay here until your father comes home. Okay? Okay?

821
01:10:47,827 --> 01:10:51,831
小美呀
Mei!

822
01:10:55,422 --> 01:10:57,879
小美
Mei!

823
01:11:00,135 --> 01:11:02,884
小美
Mei!

824
01:11:05,015 --> 01:11:07,101
小美回来了没？
- Did she come back?    - No.

825
01:11:06,846 --> 01:11:10,396
没在公车站牌那边吗？
- She wasn't at the bus stop?    - No.

826
01:11:10,562 --> 01:11:11,851
这就奇怪了
Let's think.

827
01:11:11,605 --> 01:11:13,853
她会跑到哪里去了？
Do you know anywhere else she might have gone?

828
01:11:13,895 --> 01:11:15,834
我刚刚跟小美吵了一架
I yelled at her this morning. She wanted Mom to come home.

829
01:11:15,834 --> 01:11:17,773
因为她⋯
I yelled at her this morning. She wanted Mom to come home.

830
01:11:17,778 --> 01:11:20,739
她会不会　跑去妈妈住的医院了
Granny, I bet she went to see Mom at the hospital!

831
01:11:20,818 --> 01:11:23,696
七国山医院去了呀
You think she'd try to walk to the hospital?

832
01:11:23,200 --> 01:11:26,741
可是就连大人也得　走上三个钟头才会到
Why, that's a three-hour walk even for grown-ups.

833
01:11:26,412 --> 01:11:28,701
我去看看
I'll go look.

834
01:11:29,660 --> 01:11:33,748
勘太　快点去叫你爸爸回来
Kanta! Hurry! Run on home and get your father!

835
01:11:33,127 --> 01:11:36,834
小美不见了
Mei's disappeared, and we need all the help we can get!

836
01:11:44,967 --> 01:11:48,721
小美真是笨蛋　不知道路又爱乱跑
I shouldn't have yelled at her. This is all my fault.

837
01:11:55,566 --> 01:11:58,856
小美
Mei!

838
01:12:04,658 --> 01:12:08,032
打搅了，伯伯，请问⋯⋯
Excuse me, mister! Hello!

839
01:12:07,578 --> 01:12:11,744
您有没有看见束辫子的小女孩　从这条路经过
- Yeah?    - I'm looking for my sister.

840
01:12:10,539 --> 01:12:13,167
她是我妹妹
Did you happen to see a little girl pass this way?

841
01:12:13,334 --> 01:12:16,045
这个嘛⋯⋯小女孩啊
Let's see. Uh, a little girl?

842
01:12:16,211 --> 01:12:19,798
没什么印象
Mmm, I don't think so. I would have noticed.

843
01:12:19,835 --> 01:12:21,921
她会不会没往这边来
I'll try the other road.

844
01:12:40,569 --> 01:12:43,109
妳确定她是往这边来的？
MAN: Are you sure that this is the way she came?

845
01:12:43,155 --> 01:12:45,111
我也不知道
I don't know.

846
01:12:52,915 --> 01:12:55,705
小美
Mei!

847
01:12:56,502 --> 01:12:59,088
(HEAVY BREATHING)

848
01:13:16,522 --> 01:13:19,233
停车！
Stop! Please, stop!

849
01:13:20,984 --> 01:13:22,379
搞什么啊！危险啊
- Oh! Are you crazy?    - I'm looking for my little sister.

850
01:13:22,379 --> 01:13:23,774
我在找我妹妹
- Oh! Are you crazy?    - I'm looking for my little sister.

851
01:13:23,487 --> 01:13:26,198
你们有没有看一个小女孩
Have you seen a girl walking this way?

852
01:13:25,901 --> 01:13:27,695
妳妹妹？
Is she lost?

853
01:13:27,491 --> 01:13:29,616
她好像是往七国山医院去了
I think she's trying to walk to the hospital. She's only four years old.

854
01:13:29,616 --> 01:13:31,741
她是一个四岁的小女孩
I think she's trying to walk to the hospital. She's only four years old.

855
01:13:31,578 --> 01:13:34,039
良子啊，你刚才有没有看到
Oh. I didn't see her. Did you?

856
01:13:34,206 --> 01:13:36,746
我们两个　就是从那个方向来的
No. We just came from the hospital,

857
01:13:36,500 --> 01:13:39,962
不过　好像没有看到那样的小孩
and there was no sign of a little girl on the road.

858
01:13:39,790 --> 01:13:42,423
谢谢你们
Okay. Thanks.

859
01:13:42,589 --> 01:13:45,134
你从哪里来的？
- Wait. Where'd you say you're from?    - From Matsugo.

860
01:13:44,712 --> 01:13:45,838
松乡
Matsugo! Ho!

861
01:13:45,838 --> 01:13:46,964
松乡！？
Matsugo! Ho!

862
01:13:46,927 --> 01:13:49,847
会不会搞错了呀
A four-year-old couldn't walk this far.

863
01:13:49,972 --> 01:13:50,931
(ENGINE STARTS)

864
01:13:50,760 --> 01:13:52,891
就是啊
MAN: Good luck. I hope you find her.

865
01:14:03,152 --> 01:14:05,232
小月
Satsuki!

866
01:14:06,238 --> 01:14:08,615
勘太
Kanta!

867
01:14:09,283 --> 01:14:10,529
怎么样？
- Find her?    - No.

868
01:14:10,325 --> 01:14:12,740
没看到，那妳呢？
- I guess you didn't, either.    - Mmm-mmm.

869
01:14:12,744 --> 01:14:15,080
现在我爸爸他们也去找了
My dad's got a bunch of people looking for her.

870
01:14:14,867 --> 01:14:17,578
我去往七国山的路上看看
I could ride my bike to the hospital for you.

871
01:14:17,662 --> 01:14:19,960
妳先回家去
- You should go back home.    - Check all around.

872
01:14:19,288 --> 01:14:20,636
我想小美一定是想去医院
I'm sure that Mei got lost on her way to the hospital, okay?

873
01:14:20,636 --> 01:14:21,985
可是却走错路了
I'm sure that Mei got lost on her way to the hospital, okay?

874
01:14:21,985 --> 01:14:23,334
一定是
I'm sure that Mei got lost on her way to the hospital, okay?

875
01:14:23,464 --> 01:14:26,796
刚才有人在神池　发现一只小孩的凉鞋
A little while ago, they found a sandal in the pond.

876
01:14:30,012 --> 01:14:32,014
(GASPS)

877
01:14:33,390 --> 01:14:36,555
不过还不确定　那就是小美的鞋子
They don't know for sure it's Mei's sandal!

878
01:14:53,160 --> 01:14:54,949
找到了吗？
Did you find her yet?

879
01:15:18,977 --> 01:15:20,395
MAN: We'll check the irrigation ditch.

880
01:15:20,562 --> 01:15:23,899
(PEOPLE CHATTERING)

881
01:15:24,566 --> 01:15:26,401
MAN: On the far end.

882
01:15:26,568 --> 01:15:30,901
喃呒阿弥陀佛
(CHANTING)

883
01:15:30,943 --> 01:15:34,739
池那边泥比较深一点　从那边开始啊
It's much deeper over there. You should try there first!

884
01:15:34,368 --> 01:15:36,699
递根竹竿给我！
MAN: Are there more poles?

885
01:15:44,253 --> 01:15:45,351
喃呒阿弥陀佛　婆婆，小月来了
(CHANTING)

886
01:15:45,351 --> 01:15:46,449
喃呒阿弥陀佛　婆婆，小月来了
(CLAMORING)

887
01:15:46,449 --> 01:15:47,548
喃呒阿弥陀佛　婆婆，小月来了
Huh?

888
01:15:49,049 --> 01:15:50,926
WOMAN: It's Satsuki.

889
01:15:51,756 --> 01:15:53,799
婆婆

890
01:15:54,137 --> 01:15:56,886
妳看看这个
Here. Is this Mei's?

891
01:16:05,482 --> 01:16:08,318
不是小美的
- It's not hers.    - Oh!

892
01:16:08,443 --> 01:16:10,320
(SIGHS)

893
01:16:12,656 --> 01:16:14,074
Ohh…

894
01:16:14,241 --> 01:16:15,242
(SIGHS)

895
01:16:16,952 --> 01:16:19,700
太好了
Oh, thank goodness.

896
01:16:18,912 --> 01:16:22,828
我还以　这是小美的
I was positively certain that sandal belonged to Mei.

897
01:16:22,791 --> 01:16:25,790
婆婆就爱穷紧张
All right. Granny just got carried away.

898
01:16:24,918 --> 01:16:27,917
虚惊一场啊
Hey! It's not her sandal!

899
01:16:27,958 --> 01:16:29,752
那孩子到底跑到哪去了？

900
01:16:29,794 --> 01:16:30,878
再去四处找找

901
01:16:30,961 --> 01:16:32,797
快点啊，天要黑了

902
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:35,361
不好意思啊
All right everyone, I know you've spent a lot of time here already,

903
01:16:35,361 --> 01:16:37,843
大家辛苦你们　再回头去找找好了
All right everyone, I know you've spent a lot of time here already,

904
01:16:35,929 --> 01:16:37,848
but we still need your help.

905
01:17:04,583 --> 01:17:05,626
Please.

906
01:17:05,792 --> 01:17:07,961
求求你们
(PANTING)

907
01:17:07,998 --> 01:17:10,297
把我带去龙猫那里
Let me in to see Totoro. Mei's lost.

908
01:17:09,875 --> 01:17:11,668
我的妹妹走丢了
It's getting dark, and she's out there all alone.

909
01:17:11,668 --> 01:17:13,462
不久天就要黑了
It's getting dark, and she's out there all alone.

910
01:17:13,175 --> 01:17:15,965
她一定在哪里迷了路
Please let me in to see him. It's an emergency.

911
01:17:39,242 --> 01:17:40,160
(THUDDING)

912
01:17:40,327 --> 01:17:41,328
(SCREAMING)

913
01:17:41,495 --> 01:17:44,915
(THUDDING)

914
01:17:45,082 --> 01:17:46,208
(GASPS)

915
01:17:46,375 --> 01:17:47,997
大龙猫？
Totoro!

916
01:17:49,628 --> 01:17:51,058
大龙猫
Totoro, Mei's lost. I looked everywhere for her, but I couldn't find her.

917
01:17:51,058 --> 01:17:52,488
我妹妹小美走失了
Totoro, Mei's lost. I looked everywhere for her, but I couldn't find her.

918
01:17:52,488 --> 01:17:53,919
我找了好久都找不到
Totoro, Mei's lost. I looked everywhere for her, but I couldn't find her.

919
01:17:53,924 --> 01:17:56,839
求求你，帮我找小美好不好
Please help me. I have to find her.

920
01:17:57,006 --> 01:18:00,759
她一定已经吓哭了
I'm sure she's scared half to death by now.

921
01:18:00,764 --> 01:18:03,099
我现在不知道该怎么办好
I don't know where else to turn.

922
01:18:03,099 --> 01:18:05,435
我现在不知道该怎么办好
(SOBBING)

923
01:19:01,946 --> 01:19:04,198
大家都看不到它
No one else can see it, can they?

924
01:20:12,437 --> 01:20:14,606
(LAUGHING)

925
01:20:15,728 --> 01:20:17,076
小美
GRANNY: Mei!

926
01:20:17,076 --> 01:20:18,424
小美
(GASP)

927
01:20:18,424 --> 01:20:19,773
小美
Mei!

928
01:20:27,077 --> 01:20:29,742
树林开出了一条路了
The trees are parting!

929
01:20:58,692 --> 01:21:00,694
(SIGHS)

930
01:21:00,814 --> 01:21:02,816
小美
SATSUKI: Mei!

931
01:21:05,903 --> 01:21:09,786
姊姊
Satsuki!

932
01:21:09,948 --> 01:21:13,081
姊姊
- Where are you?    - Mei!

933
01:21:12,743 --> 01:21:13,952
小美

934
01:21:23,212 --> 01:21:24,755
小美
- Mei!    - Satsuki!

935
01:21:24,755 --> 01:21:26,298
姊姊
- Mei!    - Satsuki!

936
01:21:28,013 --> 01:21:30,158
妳这个傻瓜
- Oh! You're okay.    - I'm sorry.

937
01:21:30,158 --> 01:21:32,304
对不起
- Oh! You're okay.    - I'm sorry.

938
01:21:33,852 --> 01:21:36,083
妳是不是想要把粟米　送去医院给妈妈？
Were you trying to take your corn to Mom at the hospital?

939
01:21:36,083 --> 01:21:38,315
妳是不是想要把粟米　送去医院给妈妈？
Mmm-hmm.

940
01:21:38,481 --> 01:21:42,527
(YOWLING)

941
01:21:45,196 --> 01:21:47,986
〝七国山医院〞
HOSPITAL

942
01:21:49,409 --> 01:21:51,912
你要送我们去医院吗？
You're going to take us to the hospital?

943
01:21:53,951 --> 01:21:55,559
谢谢你
Thank you!

944
01:21:55,559 --> 01:21:57,167
谢谢你
(LAUGHING)

945
01:22:04,215 --> 01:22:07,427
对不起，只不过是感冒
I'm sorry. I don't know why the hospital sent a telegram.

946
01:22:07,047 --> 01:22:09,842
医院就擅自决定　发电报给家里了
It's just a cold.

947
01:22:09,512 --> 01:22:11,973
那两个孩子一定都很担心我吧
I hope it didn't upset the girls too much. I've caused them enough grief already.

948
01:22:11,973 --> 01:22:14,434
真是苦了她们了
I hope it didn't upset the girls too much. I've caused them enough grief already.

949
01:22:14,601 --> 01:22:17,062
她们知道你平安就会安心的
When they see you're all right, they'll be fine.

950
01:22:17,015 --> 01:22:20,023
这些年来我们一家四口
We'll just wait a little longer for a weekend together.

951
01:22:18,934 --> 01:22:20,727
不都这样努力过来的吗？

952
01:22:20,190 --> 01:22:23,568
享福之前总得吃点苦啊
Don't worry. We've made it this far.

953
01:22:23,735 --> 01:22:27,025
她们表面好像没事　可是心里一定很难过
The girls act so strong, but I think it's been harder than they let on.

954
01:22:27,113 --> 01:22:28,239
Especially Satsuki.

955
01:22:27,776 --> 01:22:32,953
小月越是懂事　就越教人于心不忍
- She tries to act so adult.    - That's true.

956
01:22:31,780 --> 01:22:33,031
是啊

957
01:22:33,119 --> 01:22:35,868
出院以后我一定要好好疼她们
I can't wait until I get better.

958
01:22:34,746 --> 01:22:38,036
让她们尽情耍耍小脾气
When I get home, I'm going to spoil those girls rotten.

959
01:22:37,624 --> 01:22:38,625
(LAUGHING)

960
01:22:38,792 --> 01:22:40,460
(INAUDIBLE)

961
01:22:45,799 --> 01:22:48,172
妈妈在笑
Look at Mom. She's laughing.

962
01:22:47,842 --> 01:22:50,720
看样子是没事了
- Everything must be okay.    - Yeah.

963
01:22:58,390 --> 01:23:00,976
我得赶快把身体养好才行
I'm going to hurry up and get well!

964
01:23:00,605 --> 01:23:03,233
是啊
That's the spirit. Huh?

965
01:23:10,240 --> 01:23:11,760
是谁摆的啊？
Who left this?

966
01:23:11,760 --> 01:23:13,280
是谁摆的啊？
(GASPS)

967
01:23:13,618 --> 01:23:14,990
怎么啦？
What is it?

968
01:23:15,286 --> 01:23:19,411
我好像看到小月和小美坐在那棵松树上笑
I thought I saw Satsuki and Mei smiling at us from up in that tree.

969
01:23:21,543 --> 01:23:23,790
搞不好是真的也说不定啊
It sounds crazy, but maybe you did.

970
01:23:23,874 --> 01:23:25,917
妳看
- Look at this.    - “For Mommy.”

971
01:23:25,917 --> 01:23:27,961
〝送给妈妈〞
- Look at this.    - “For Mommy.”

972
01:23:29,759 --> 01:23:33,263
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

973
01:23:33,430 --> 01:23:36,641
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

